expo.name: GSLP: 8 Weeks
expo.description: GSLP is a popular training program based around compound exercises. I didnt find an app I liked and thought I'd make my own. Fitness icons are from icons8.com, and most photos are by the talented Alora Griffiths (https://unsplash.com/@aloragriffiths) and Leon Martinez (https://www.pexels.com/@leon-martinez-714926)
